high_descs: Turn right, walk forward one step, then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the credit card from the table.
Place the card in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the card.
Turn right, walk across the room, turn right again, walk to the chair, then turn right and walk until you hit the table.
Place the bowl on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move the bowl and the credit card to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn and go to the right side of the table you are currently facing.
Pick up the red credit card that is on the table.
Place the credit card in the grey bowl that is in front of you on the table.
Pick up the bowl with the credit card in it.
With the bowl with the credit card in hand turn and go to the coffee table with the couch on your left side face the coffee table.
Place the bowl with the credit card behind the object that is on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Move bowl with credit card to coffee table.

high_descs: Take a step ahead and right.
Pick up the red credit card.
Place the credit card in the bowl.
Turn right and walk to the garbage, then turn right again. Walk to the chair in the corner then turn right and walk to the coffee table.
Place the bowl on the coffee table to the left of the tissues.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a credit card in it on a coffee table.
